AND PEOPLE ARE COMPLETELY

11:46.606 --> 11:47.974
DEVOTED TO THE COMPANY AND THE

11:47.974 --> 11:50.243
REST OF THEIR LIFE FALLS AWAY.

11:50.243 --> 11:52.779
THE UNIQUE THING WITH AMAZON IS,

11:52.779 --> 11:54.647
THEY HAD PRESERVED TO A LARGE

11:54.647 --> 11:59.218
EXTENT THAT START-UP CULTURE, TO

11:59.218 --> 12:01.654
A COMPANY THAT WAS EMPLOYING

12:01.654 --> 12:04.557
TENS OF THOUSANDS OF PEOPLE.

12:04.557 --> 12:06.426
AND THAT'S A REMARKABLE THING TO

12:06.426 --> 12:08.061
DO, AND I DON'T KNOW OF MANY

12:08.061 --> 12:09.495
OTHER COMPANIES, IF ANY, THAT

12:09.495 --> 12:11.331
HAVE MANAGED TO DO IT.

