>> AMAZON USES A TECHNIQUE WHICH

13:02.215 --> 13:05.718
WAS RELATIVELY WIDESPREAD IN

13:05.718 --> 13:07.687
CORPORATE AMERICA MAYBE TEN

13:07.687 --> 13:08.721
YEARS AGO.

