AND WITHOUT IT BEING -- WITHOUT

13:54.701 --> 13:56.235
THOSE HIGH STANDARDS, YOU

13:56.235 --> 13:58.371
PROBABLY NEVER WOULD HAVE HEARD

13:58.371 --> 13:59.772
OF AMAZON.

